item.description:
I am dedicating the first Tuesday of each month to helping you to learn more about paper crafting or completing your current projects.  Bring your current project and you will have access to my inks, stamps, Big Shot and dies.  I also have hundred of card and scrapbooking ideas for inspiration.

New to card making or scrapbooking??  Contact me with your thoughts on what you would like to learn and I will put some ideas together for you.  I am a Stampin' Up! demonstrator and have card kits available.

Cost is $5 or waived if you purchase a kit.  Check out my kits here on my website.

You can also check out more project ideas and view my artwork on my blog at:

www.jeanne-nielsen.blogspot.com/

I hope to see you soon!

 

Jeanne
item.how_to_find_us: Jeanne's Crafting Corner - 7 Heritage Lane, Lynnfield, MA -- right off Main Street which is off of Route 128/95.
item.name: Open Stamping and Scrapbooking
